member.name: OLECONTF
member.summary: Indicates the type of objects to be enumerated.

member.name: OLECONTF.OLECONTF_EMBEDDINGS
member.summary: Enumerates the embedded objects in the container.

member.name: OLECONTF.OLECONTF_LINKS
member.summary: Enumerates the linked objects in the container.

member.name: OLECONTF.OLECONTF_OTHERS
member.summary: Enumerates all objects in the container that are not OLE compound document objects (i.e., objects other than linked or embedded objects). Use this flag to enumerate the container's pseudo-objects.

member.name: OLECONTF.OLECONTF_ONLYUSER
member.summary: Enumerates only those objects the user is aware of. For example, hidden named-ranges in Microsoft Excel would not be enumerated using this value.

member.name: OLECONTF.OLECONTF_ONLYIFRUNNING
member.summary: Enumerates only those linked or embedded objects that are currently in the running state for this container.
